pg-roaringbitmap (1.2.0-1.pscale1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial PlanetScale build of pg_roaringbitmap.
  * Includes upstream fix hardening validation of untrusted bitmap blobs
    in the recv functions (bounds all deserialization by the BYTEA length).
  * Support for PostgreSQL 17-18.

